---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms & Privacy | InstantCompany.com" description="Terms of Service and Privacy Policy for InstantCompany.com.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative w-full rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden bg-[#0f1115] text-white p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-200">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0f1115] via-[#0f1115]/90 to-[#0f1115]/80 absolute inset-0"></div>
    </div>
    <Header />
    <div class="relative z-10 mt-16 max-w-3xl pb-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl text-white mb-4 font-manrope font-medium tracking-tighter">Terms & Privacy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">Last updated: March 1, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none prose-headings:font-manrope prose-headings:tracking-tighter prose-headings:font-medium prose-a:text-emerald-600 prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:text-emerald-700">

        <h2>Terms of Service</h2>

        <h3>1. Acceptance of Terms</h3>
        <p>
          By accessing or using InstantCompany.com ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Service.
        </p>

        <h3>2. Description of Service</h3>
        <p>
          InstantCompany.com is an AI-powered business idea generation platform. The Service generates brand names, positioning statements, pricing frameworks, marketing copy, and other business-related content based on user input.
        </p>

        <h3>3. AI-Generated Content Disclaimer</h3>
        <p>
          All content generated by InstantCompany is created by artificial intelligence and is intended for <strong>inspirational and strategic starting purposes only</strong>. Generated content should not be considered professional business, legal, or financial advice. Users are responsible for validating all generated content before use.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Brand names and domain suggestions may already be registered or trademarked by third parties.</li>
          <li>Pricing recommendations are based on AI analysis and should be validated with market research.</li>
          <li>Business strategies should be reviewed by qualified professionals before significant investment.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>4. User Responsibilities</h3>
        <p>
          You agree to use the Service only for lawful purposes. You are solely responsible for any business decisions made based on content generated by the Service. InstantCompany does not guarantee the success of any business venture based on generated content.
        </p>

        <h3>5. Intellectual Property</h3>
        <p>
          Content generated by the Service for your use belongs to you. However, similar or identical content may be generated for other users. The InstantCompany brand, website design, and underlying technology remain the property of InstantCompany.
        </p>

        <h3>6. Limitation of Liability</h3>
        <p>
          InstantCompany is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Service, including but not limited to business losses, lost profits, or reputational damage.
        </p>

        <h3>7. Modifications</h3>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
        </p>

        <div class="h-px bg-gray-200 my-12"></div>

        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

        <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Input Data:</strong> The business ideas and concepts you submit to the generator.</li>
          <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Email address and name if you create an account.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, features used, and general interaction patterns.</li>
          <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Browser type, operating system, and device type for optimization purposes.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p>Your information is used to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Generate business blueprints and deliver the Service.</li>
          <li>Improve the quality and accuracy of AI-generated output.</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about your account or the Service.</li>
          <li>Analyze usage patterns to improve the product experience.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>3. Data Retention</h3>
        <p>
          Business ideas submitted to the generator may be retained to improve our AI models. Generated output is stored in your account if you have one. You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us.
        </p>

        <h3>4. Data Sharing</h3>
        <p>
          We do not sell your personal information. We may share anonymized, aggregated data for analytics purposes. We may disclose information if required by law or to protect the rights and safety of our users.
        </p>

        <h3>5. Security</h3>
        <p>
          We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data, including encryption in transit and at rest. However, no system is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </p>

        <h3>6. Your Rights</h3>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data.</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing communications.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>7. Contact</h3>
        <p>
          For questions about these terms or our privacy practices, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@instantcompany.com">hello@instantcompany.com</a> or visit our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
